                   Requirements & Installation
                  =============================
   System Requirements: PAL AMIGA 1200 + 6+ MEGABYTES FREE HD SPACE.
   FTLOM uses "lowlevel.library" This should be in Sys:Libs/.
   To play FTLOM just de-archive to your Selected Partition
   & click on For.The.Love.of.Money Icon.

   Your hard drive should contain the following files-:

   FTLOM_DEMO (DIR)
   For.The.Love.of.Money (FILE)&.info
   FTLOM.docs (FILE)&.info

